@chelle_roc sneak peek @kennygdmv 💍 
#engagement #engaged💍

Man o man where do I start? This birthday was made special due to my wonderful lady providing me with such an experience a man could never forget. She brought together family and friends from all over to make my birthday a special one. It felt good to actually be surprised and not be the one doing all the surprising 😂

Funny thing is I was planning her entire birthday party while she was planning mine. I’m the one who actually does events she’s never done anything like this in her life and it came out PERFECT! I’m so proud of her and appreciate her for all her efforts. The details were not to be overlooked!

Thank you to all my loved ones who made the experience that much better. The gifts, the money showers, the endless laughs, the love was evident! This was one for the books. 

One word - Gratitude 💫

-Your Fav 🦂

Where are my devoted couples at? Doing something different for the culture. This is my effort to change the narrative in 2023 and beyond that couples cannot have fun in the club, as well as that toxic narrative needs to change!

There are some amazing beautiful couples that love to enjoy the aspects of nightlife w/o the drama and toxicity that follows. Let’s help shift the focus by bringing you this edition of So Long To Tha Streets. 🥂
